channel.name: CBBC UK
channel.title: Boy Girl Dog Cat Mouse Cheese
channel.desc: Cheese takes up the bagpipes and, while nobody else can stand the sound, a group of squirrels becomes strangely entranced by it. They like it so much that they follow Cheese wherever she goes and grow restless, whiny and destructive whenever she tries to stop playing. Can the gang help poor Cheese get her old quiet life back.
